sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as Administrateur
    participant Browser as Navigateur
    participant Gateway as API Gateway
    participant OrderSvc as Order Service
    participant EventSvc as Event Service
    participant AuthSvc as Auth Service
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Admin->>Browser: Accède à /admin
    Browser->>Gateway: GET /api/orders/stats/overview
    Browser->>Gateway: GET /api/events/stats/overview
    Browser->>Gateway: GET /api/auth/users?limit=5

    par Statistiques commandes
        Gateway->>OrderSvc: Forward request
        OrderSvc->>DB: SELECT COUNT, SUM, AVG
        DB-->>OrderSvc: Données agrégées
        OrderSvc-->>Gateway: { totalOrders, revenue, avgOrder, ... }
        Gateway-->>Browser: 200 OK
    and Statistiques événements
        Gateway->>EventSvc: Forward request
        EventSvc->>DB: SELECT COUNT, GROUP BY status
        DB-->>EventSvc: Données agrégées
        EventSvc-->>Gateway: { totalEvents, quotes, conversion, ... }
        Gateway-->>Browser: 200 OK
    and Liste utilisateurs
        Gateway->>AuthSvc: Forward request
        AuthSvc->>DB: SELECT users ORDER BY created_at
        DB-->>AuthSvc: Derniers utilisateurs
        AuthSvc-->>Gateway: { users: [...] }
        Gateway-->>Browser: 200 OK
    end

    Browser->>Admin: Affichage KPI cards + graphiques
